messages.messageBody:
Wanna do some dumpster-diving here? :-). We have one of the highest
concentrations of grow-ops in the Vancouver area, mostly in huge expensive
houses, which the growers pay for in cash!

Robin B.
in scofflaw White Rock, B.C.
